		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">香港中环 28 平米公寓，浴缸、猫和基本需求都放得下</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-27 13:22:42 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">17</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">91</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/26084.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26084/indexMediumPc2/26084.jpg?1461735838" alt="「这世界」麦当劳汉堡十年不烂的俗梗和肯尼亚女孩">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
